import React from 'react';

const Spinner = () => (
    <svg
        className='spinner'
        width='65px'
        height='65px'
        viewBox='0 0 66 66'
        xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
    >
        <circle
            className='path'
            fill='none'
            strokeWidth='6'
            strokeLinecap='round'
            cx='33'
            cy='33'
            r='30'
        ></circle>
    </svg>
);

export default Spinner;
